{"tid":163571,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【波台音樂】《七季》－那年三冠王國米，你還記得嗎？","createTime":"2017-03-20T05:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T19:05:50.000Z","uid":15846,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02fdca989eabb5718882f779e95d28eb862f3e4e","tid":163571,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"【波台音樂】《七季》－那年三冠王國米，你還記得嗎？<br />\n<br />\n09-10球季歐冠，大家仲有啲咩印象？係咪未退化嘅摩佬？定係米列圖cup過再射？每每有人講起近年歐聯冠軍球隊都會有人提國米。可惜國米「中興」時間短，摩佬走咗之後嘅國米一季衰過一季，甚至已經幾年無打入歐冠。<br />\n<br />\n三冠王成全城佳話，但係轉眼即逝。摩佬之後，換帥快過食菜；J辛、大米都退役了；班主換咗兩次，依加仲比蘇寧買咗。但點解就係見唔返當日嘅國米？<br />\n<br />\n呢首歌就係講當年嘅三冠王國米，同埋三冠後七年嘅路，小弟唔係好叻整片同寫詞，但希望大家喜歡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《七季》</span></strong><br />\n曲：《回到過去》<br />\n主唱：挽歌之聲<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/singtosay/?fref=ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsingtosay%2F%3Ffref%3Dts&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=56acf3c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/singtosay/?fref=ts</a><br />\n詞：古亞連<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GLChannel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGLChannel%2F&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=7ed38221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GLChannel/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KdZkLdDEibE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKdZkLdDEibE&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=876d6b1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KdZkLdDEibE</a></div>"},{"pid":"a82e8dc34f6c06d988bdd85b17596d3bc71bad43","tid":163571,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T05:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a146c844a57c8ad8a0d7e755fa5b65446aaedd6","tid":163571,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s